notes.note:
Good evening Colleen, thank you for sending the revised estimate for the transmission replacement on Letisha's Journey. Fortunately the transmission replacement is a covered repair. Please be advised, as always, the customer is responsible for any diagnostic fees, shop supplies and fluids, as well as a $100 deductible + tax. Additionally, Letisha's contract covers her for a maximum of $130/h, and our Mitchell Labour Guide displays the transmission replacement as 8.8 hours, so this is the labour we will be authorizing for the repair. If you choose to charge the quoted labour for this repair, the customer will be responsible for the difference. The payout is as follows:

Parts-$2550.00
Labour-$1144.00 (8.8 x $130/h)
Deductible-$100.00 + tax 
Tax-$467.22
Authorization-BCNU9ELNP4

Total = $4061.22

Once the repair is complete, please send us a copy of the final invoice for payment.

Best regards, 

Matthew Puls
Claims Adjuster
